<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>认知智能体记忆系统架构设计</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            background: #020617;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .title-line {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .pulsing-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background: #22d3ee;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .diagram-section {
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .section-title .dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .diagram-container {
            background: #020617;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .diagram-container svg {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .card-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .card-dot.cyan { background: #22d3ee; }
        .card-dot.emerald { background: #34d399; }
        .card-dot.violet { background: #a78bfa; }
        .card-dot.rose { background: #fb7185; }
        .card-dot.orange { background: #fb923c; }
        .card-dot.slate { background: #94a3b8; }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .card li {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 12px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card li:before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .flow-diagram {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .flow-step {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }

        .flow-step-box {
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .flow-step-number {
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: 20px;
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #22d3ee;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .flow-step-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-top: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .flow-step-desc {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .flow-arrow {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-width: 40px;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .flow-arrow svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .legend {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .legend-box {
            width: 24px;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1.5px solid;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="title-line">
                <div class="pulsing-dot"></div>
                <h1>认知智能体记忆系统架构设计</h1>
            </div>
            <p class="subtitle">Cognitive Memory System Architecture • 基于 OceanBase 的三级记忆架构</p>
        </header>

        <!-- 整体架构设计 -->
        <section class="diagram-section">
            <div class="section-title">
                <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                <span>整体架构设计 (System Architecture)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-container">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 720" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <!-- Background Grid -->
                    <defs>
                        <pattern id="grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                            <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                        </pattern>
                        <marker id="arrowhead" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                            <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#64748b"/>
                        </marker>
                    </defs>
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)"/>

                    <!-- Connection Arrows (drawn first to appear behind) -->
                    <!-- ESP32 to WebSocket -->
                    <line x1="200" y1="100" x2="400" y2="100" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                    <!-- WebSocket to Memory -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="130" x2="600" y2="180" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                    <!-- Memory to OceanBase -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="450" x2="600" y2="520" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                    <!-- Memory to LLM -->
                    <line x1="750" y1="315" x2="880" y2="315" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                    <!-- Manager-API to Memory -->
                    <line x1="1000" y1="100" x2="750" y2="180" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

                    <!-- External Systems -->
                    <!-- ESP32 Device -->
                    <rect x="40" y="70" width="160" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="40" y="70" width="160" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(8, 51, 68, 0.4)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="120" y="95" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">ESP32 Device</text>
                    <text x="120" y="112" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">WebSocket Client</text>

                    <!-- Manager API -->
                    <rect x="1000" y="70" width="160" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="1000" y="70" width="160" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="1080" y="95" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Manager API</text>
                    <text x="1080" y="112" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Config Provider</text>

                    <!-- LLM Services -->
                    <rect x="880" y="285" width="280" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="880" y="285" width="280" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.3)" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="1020" y="310" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">LLM Services</text>
                    <text x="1020" y="327" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Qwen / OpenAI / Custom LLM</text>

                    <!-- WebSocket Server -->
                    <rect x="400" y="70" width="200" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="70" width="200" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="500" y="95" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">WebSocket Server</text>
                    <text x="500" y="112" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Port 8000</text>

                    <!-- Cognitive Memory Framework -->
                    <rect x="250" y="180" width="700" height="270" rx="12" fill="none" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="8,4"/>
                    <text x="300" y="205" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="13" font-weight="600">自研认知记忆框架 (Cognitive Memory Framework)</text>

                    <!-- Memory Provider Factory -->
                    <rect x="450" y="225" width="300" height="40" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="450" y="225" width="300" height="40" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="250" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">MemoryProviderFactory</text>

                    <!-- Multi-Level Memory -->
                    <rect x="270" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="270" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="370" y="312" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">多级记忆架构</text>

                    <!-- Level 1 -->
                    <rect x="290" y="325" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="370" y="343" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Level 1: 语义记忆</text>

                    <!-- Level 2 -->
                    <rect x="290" y="358" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="370" y="376" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Level 2: 情景记忆</text>

                    <!-- Level 3 -->
                    <rect x="290" y="391" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="370" y="409" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Level 3: 程序记忆</text>

                    <!-- Intelligent Lifecycle -->
                    <rect x="500" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="500" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="312" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">智能生命周期引擎</text>

                    <!-- Extraction -->
                    <rect x="520" y="325" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="343" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">智能抽取 (LLM驱动)</text>

                    <!-- Merging -->
                    <rect x="520" y="358" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="376" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">智能合并 (去重)</text>

                    <!-- Forgetting -->
                    <rect x="520" y="391" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="409" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">遗忘曲线 (艾宾浩斯)</text>

                    <!-- Retrieval Engine -->
                    <rect x="730" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="730" y="290" width="200" height="140" rx="6" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="830" y="312" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">记忆检索引擎</text>

                    <!-- Hybrid Search -->
                    <rect x="750" y="325" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.3)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="830" y="343" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">混合检索策略</text>

                    <!-- Ranking -->
                    <rect x="750" y="358" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.3)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="830" y="376" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">结果排序融合</text>

                    <!-- Context -->
                    <rect x="750" y="391" width="160" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.3)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="830" y="409" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">上下文格式化</text>

                    <!-- OceanBase Database -->
                    <rect x="300" y="520" width="600" height="150" rx="8" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="300" y="520" width="600" height="150" rx="8" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="600" y="545" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">OceanBase Database</text>
                    <text x="600" y="562" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">Port 2881 • Vector + Graph Storage</text>

                    <!-- Vector Store -->
                    <rect x="330" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="330" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="415" y="605" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">向量存储</text>
                    <text x="415" y="622" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">memories 表</text>
                    <text x="415" y="637" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">IVF_FLAT 索引</text>

                    <!-- Graph Store -->
                    <rect x="515" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="515" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="605" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">知识图谱存储</text>
                    <text x="600" y="622" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">user_memories 表</text>
                    <text x="600" y="637" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">graph_edges 表</text>

                    <!-- Profile Store -->
                    <rect x="700" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="700" y="580" width="170" height="70" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="785" y="605" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">用户画像存储</text>
                    <text x="785" y="622" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">user_profiles 表</text>
                    <text x="785" y="637" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">记忆宫殿</text>

                    <!-- Legend -->
                    <g transform="translate(40, 690)">
                        <rect width="1120" height="24" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>

                        <rect x="15" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(8, 51, 68, 0.4)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="42" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Frontend</text>

                        <rect x="110" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="137" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Backend</text>

                        <rect x="205" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="232" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Database/Memory</text>

                        <rect x="345" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.3)" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="372" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Cloud/LLM</text>

                        <rect x="450" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="477" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Processing</text>

                        <rect x="570" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="597" y="16" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">Security/Retrieval</text>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                        <h3>多级记忆架构</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>语义记忆：</strong>基于向量检索，存储事实和知识</li>
                        <li><strong>情景记忆：</strong>基于知识图谱，存储事件和关系</li>
                        <li><strong>程序记忆：</strong>用户画像存储，长期特征持久化</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot orange"></div>
                        <h3>智能生命周期管理</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>智能抽取：</strong>LLM驱动的显著性检测</li>
                        <li><strong>智能合并：</strong>语义去重与时间整合</li>
                        <li><strong>遗忘曲线：</strong>艾宾浩斯衰减模型</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot rose"></div>
                        <h3>混合检索引擎</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>向量检索：</strong>余弦相似度 Top-K</li>
                        <li><strong>图谱遍历：</strong>多跳关联推理</li>
                        <li><strong>画像注入：</strong>个性化上下文</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 记忆写入流程 -->
        <section class="diagram-section">
            <div class="section-title">
                <div class="card-dot emerald"></div>
                <span>记忆写入流程 (Memory Write Pipeline)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-container">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 750" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <defs>
                        <pattern id="grid2" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                            <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                        </pattern>
                        <marker id="arrowhead2" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                            <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#64748b"/>
                        </marker>
                    </defs>
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid2)"/>

                    <!-- Flow Arrows -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="80" x2="600" y2="120" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="180" x2="600" y2="220" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="280" x2="600" y2="320" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>

                    <!-- Split to three paths -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="380" x2="300" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="380" x2="600" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="380" x2="900" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>

                    <!-- Merge back -->
                    <line x1="300" y1="500" x2="600" y2="540" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="500" x2="600" y2="540" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="900" y1="500" x2="600" y2="540" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>

                    <line x1="600" y1="600" x2="600" y2="640" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="700" x2="600" y2="720" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead2)"/>

                    <!-- Trigger -->
                    <rect x="420" y="30" width="360" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="420" y="30" width="360" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(8, 51, 68, 0.4)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="55" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">触发：对话轮次完成</text>
                    <text x="600" y="70" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">(User + Assistant Messages)</text>

                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="120" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="120" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="140" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 1</text>
                    <text x="600" y="145" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">消息标准化</text>
                    <text x="600" y="162" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">过滤系统消息 | 提取纯文本 | 角色过滤</text>
                    <text x="600" y="175" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">(UserMemory模式仅保留用户消息)</text>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="220" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="220" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="240" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 2</text>
                    <text x="600" y="245" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">智能记忆抽取 (LLM驱动)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="262" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">显著性检测 | 实体提取 | 情感标记 | 上下文摘要</text>
                    <text x="600" y="275" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">识别关键信息，过滤低价值内容</text>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="320" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="320" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="340" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 3</text>
                    <text x="600" y="345" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">向量化与图谱提取</text>
                    <text x="600" y="362" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">生成1024维嵌入向量 | 提取实体关系三元组</text>
                    <text x="600" y="375" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">准备多级存储数据结构</text>

                    <!-- Parallel Processing -->
                    <!-- Vector Store -->
                    <rect x="170" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="170" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="300" y="445" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">向量存储 (语义记忆)</text>
                    <text x="300" y="462" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">INSERT INTO memories</text>
                    <text x="300" y="475" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">(memory, embedding, user_id, metadata)</text>
                    <text x="300" y="490" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">IVF_FLAT 索引自动更新</text>

                    <!-- Graph Store -->
                    <rect x="470" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="470" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="445" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">图谱存储 (情景记忆)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="462" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">INSERT INTO user_memories, graph_edges</text>
                    <text x="600" y="475" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">(subject, predicate, object, weight)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="490" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">实体关系三元组持久化</text>

                    <!-- Profile Store -->
                    <rect x="770" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="770" y="420" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="900" y="445" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">画像存储 (程序记忆)</text>
                    <text x="900" y="462" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">UPSERT INTO user_profiles</text>
                    <text x="900" y="475" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">(topics JSON / content TEXT)</text>
                    <text x="900" y="490" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">记忆宫殿更新，缓存失效</text>

                    <!-- Step 4 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="540" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="540" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="560" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 4</text>
                    <text x="600" y="565" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">智能合并与去重</text>
                    <text x="600" y="582" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">语义相似度检查 (cosine > 0.85 → 合并)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="595" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">时间整合 (1小时内记忆合并) | 冲突解决</text>

                    <!-- Step 5 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="640" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="640" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="660" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 5</text>
                    <text x="600" y="665" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">遗忘曲线应用</text>
                    <text x="600" y="682" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">艾宾浩斯衰减: R(t) = e^(-t/S)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="695" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">剪除低价值记忆 (R < 0.1) | 频繁访问增强</text>

                    <!-- Output -->
                    <rect x="400" y="720" width="400" height="30" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="720" width="400" height="30" rx="6" fill="rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5)" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="740" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">输出: profile_extracted + topics + profile_content</text>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot emerald"></div>
                        <h3>流水线特性</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>异步处理：</strong>asyncio + 线程池</li>
                        <li><strong>并行写入：</strong>三级记忆同时持久化</li>
                        <li><strong>事务保证：</strong>原子性写入或回滚</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot orange"></div>
                        <h3>智能优化</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>显著性过滤：</strong>LLM评分 < 0.3 丢弃</li>
                        <li><strong>语义去重：</strong>cosine > 0.85 自动合并</li>
                        <li><strong>时间压缩：</strong>1小时内活动摘要化</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                        <h3>OceanBase存储</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>向量表：</strong>memories (1024-dim embedding)</li>
                        <li><strong>图谱表：</strong>user_memories + graph_edges</li>
                        <li><strong>画像表：</strong>user_profiles (JSON/TEXT)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 记忆检索流程 -->
        <section class="diagram-section">
            <div class="section-title">
                <div class="card-dot rose"></div>
                <span>记忆检索流程 (Memory Retrieval Pipeline)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-container">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 780" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <defs>
                        <pattern id="grid3" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                            <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                        </pattern>
                        <marker id="arrowhead3" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                            <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#64748b"/>
                        </marker>
                    </defs>
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid3)"/>

                    <!-- Flow Arrows -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="60" x2="600" y2="100" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="160" x2="600" y2="200" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>

                    <!-- Split to three parallel searches -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="260" x2="300" y2="300" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="260" x2="600" y2="300" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="260" x2="900" y2="300" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>

                    <!-- Merge to fusion -->
                    <line x1="300" y1="380" x2="600" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="380" x2="600" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="900" y1="380" x2="600" y2="420" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>

                    <line x1="600" y1="480" x2="600" y2="520" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="580" x2="600" y2="620" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="680" x2="600" y2="720" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead3)"/>

                    <!-- Trigger -->
                    <rect x="420" y="10" width="360" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="420" y="10" width="360" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(8, 51, 68, 0.4)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="35" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">触发：用户查询 / 上下文注入</text>
                    <text x="600" y="50" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">(User Query or Context Injection)</text>

                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="100" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="100" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="120" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 1</text>
                    <text x="600" y="125" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">查询预处理</text>
                    <text x="600" y="142" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">提取纯文本 | 查询扩展 (同义词/改写)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="155" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">语言检测 (zh/en自动切换)</text>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="200" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="200" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="220" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 2</text>
                    <text x="600" y="225" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">并行检索策略</text>
                    <text x="600" y="242" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">同时发起三种查询：画像检索 + 向量检索 + 图谱遍历</text>
                    <text x="600" y="255" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">利用asyncio实现并行I/O</text>

                    <!-- Parallel Searches -->
                    <!-- Profile Query -->
                    <rect x="170" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="170" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="300" y="325" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">画像查询 (程序记忆)</text>
                    <text x="300" y="342" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Cache-Aside 策略</text>
                    <text x="300" y="355" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">缓存命中率 ~95%</text>
                    <text x="300" y="370" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">SELECT * FROM user_profiles</text>

                    <!-- Vector Search -->
                    <rect x="470" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="470" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="325" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">向量检索 (语义记忆)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="342" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">余弦相似度 Top-K=30</text>
                    <text x="600" y="355" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">IVF_FLAT 索引加速</text>
                    <text x="600" y="370" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">ORDER BY cosine_sim DESC</text>

                    <!-- Graph Traversal -->
                    <rect x="770" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="770" y="300" width="260" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="900" y="325" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">图谱遍历 (情景记忆)</text>
                    <text x="900" y="342" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">多跳BFS (max_hops可配置)</text>
                    <text x="900" y="355" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">实体扩展 + 关系评分</text>
                    <text x="900" y="370" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">图遍历 + 边剪枝</text>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="420" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="420" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3)" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="440" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 3</text>
                    <text x="600" y="445" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">结果融合与排序</text>
                    <text x="600" y="462" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">多信号评分: Score = α·语义 + β·时间 + γ·图谱中心性</text>
                    <text x="600" y="475" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">MMR多样性最大化 | Top-K=30筛选</text>

                    <!-- Step 4 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="520" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="520" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="540" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 4</text>
                    <text x="600" y="545" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">上下文格式化</text>
                    <text x="600" y="562" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">时间排序 (最新优先)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="575" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">分区格式：【用户画像】+【相关记忆】</text>

                    <!-- Step 5 -->
                    <rect x="400" y="620" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="620" width="400" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="420" y="640" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="10" font-weight="600">STEP 5</text>
                    <text x="600" y="645" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">时间戳注入</text>
                    <text x="600" y="662" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">[2026-05-03 14:30] 记忆内容</text>
                    <text x="600" y="675" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">支持时间范围过滤和归因追溯</text>

                    <!-- Output -->
                    <rect x="300" y="720" width="600" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="300" y="720" width="600" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.3)" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="740" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">输出：格式化记忆上下文</text>
                    <text x="600" y="757" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">注入LLM提示词 → 启用个性化响应生成</text>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot rose"></div>
                        <h3>混合检索策略</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>并行查询：</strong>asyncio并发I/O</li>
                        <li><strong>画像缓存：</strong>95%命中率</li>
                        <li><strong>向量检索：</strong>Top-K语义匹配</li>
                        <li><strong>图谱遍历：</strong>多跳关联推理</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot orange"></div>
                        <h3>融合排序算法</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>多信号评分：</strong>语义+时间+图谱</li>
                        <li><strong>MMR算法：</strong>多样性最大化</li>
                        <li><strong>Top-K筛选：</strong>保留最相关30条</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                        <h3>OceanBase查询优化</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>IVF_FLAT索引：</strong>向量检索加速</li>
                        <li><strong>B-tree索引：</strong>(user_id, created_at)</li>
                        <li><strong>图索引：</strong>(source_id, target_id)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 核心组件详解 -->
        <section class="diagram-section">
            <div class="section-title">
                <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                <span>核心组件详解 (Core Components Deep Dive)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-container">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 850" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <defs>
                        <pattern id="grid4" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                            <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                        </pattern>
                        <marker id="arrowhead4" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                            <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#64748b"/>
                        </marker>
                    </defs>
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid4)"/>

                    <!-- Connection Lines -->
                    <line x1="600" y1="50" x2="600" y2="90" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="300" y1="170" x2="440" y2="200" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="170" x2="600" y2="200" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="900" y1="170" x2="760" y2="200" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>

                    <line x1="550" y1="280" x2="350" y2="320" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="650" y1="280" x2="850" y2="320" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>

                    <line x1="300" y1="420" x2="600" y2="460" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="900" y1="420" x2="600" y2="460" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>
                    <line x1="600" y1="520" x2="600" y2="560" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead4)"/>

                    <!-- Entry Point -->
                    <rect x="420" y="10" width="360" height="40" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="420" y="10" width="360" height="40" rx="6" fill="rgba(8, 51, 68, 0.4)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="35" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">ConnectionHandler (per Device)</text>

                    <!-- Registry -->
                    <rect x="440" y="90" width="320" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="440" y="90" width="320" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="115" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">TextMessageHandlerRegistry</text>
                    <text x="600" y="132" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">消息分发器</text>
                    <text x="600" y="147" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">hello | listen | abort | iot | mcp | server | ping</text>
                    <text x="600" y="160" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">路由到对应的消息处理器</text>

                    <!-- Three Paths -->
                    <!-- Left: Config -->
                    <rect x="170" y="110" width="260" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="170" y="110" width="260" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.3)" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="300" y="135" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">ConfigLoader</text>
                    <text x="300" y="152" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">三层配置合并</text>
                    <text x="300" y="164" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">config.yaml → .config.yaml → API</text>

                    <!-- Right: Tool Handler -->
                    <rect x="770" y="110" width="260" height="60" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="770" y="110" width="260" height="60" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="900" y="135" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">UnifiedToolHandler</text>
                    <text x="900" y="152" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">工具调用协调器</text>
                    <text x="900" y="164" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">IoT | MCP | Plugin | Server MCP</text>

                    <!-- Memory Factory -->
                    <rect x="440" y="200" width="320" height="80" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="440" y="200" width="320" height="80" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="225" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">MemoryProviderFactory</text>
                    <text x="600" y="242" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">工厂模式创建Memory实例</text>
                    <text x="600" y="257" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">检测模式 (UserMemory / AsyncMemory)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="270" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">配置OceanBase方言 + SDK修复</text>

                    <!-- Split to UserMemory/AsyncMemory -->
                    <!-- UserMemory -->
                    <rect x="170" y="320" width="260" height="100" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="170" y="320" width="260" height="100" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="300" y="345" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">UserMemory Mode</text>
                    <text x="300" y="362" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">用户画像模式</text>
                    <text x="300" y="378" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• include_roles: ["user"]</text>
                    <text x="300" y="390" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• profile_type: "content"</text>
                    <text x="300" y="402" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 同步API (asyncio.to_thread)</text>
                    <text x="300" y="414" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 画像缓存优化</text>

                    <!-- AsyncMemory -->
                    <rect x="770" y="320" width="260" height="100" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="770" y="320" width="260" height="100" rx="6" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="900" y="345" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">AsyncMemory Mode</text>
                    <text x="900" y="362" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">对话记忆模式</text>
                    <text x="900" y="378" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 全量对话存储</text>
                    <text x="900" y="390" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 异步API (原生async)</text>
                    <text x="900" y="402" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 临时会话记忆</text>
                    <text x="900" y="414" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 轻量级存储</text>

                    <!-- Core Framework -->
                    <rect x="300" y="460" width="600" height="100" rx="8" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="300" y="460" width="600" height="100" rx="8" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="600" y="485" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">自研认知记忆框架 (Cognitive Memory Framework)</text>

                    <!-- Three Layers -->
                    <rect x="330" y="500" width="170" height="50" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="415" y="520" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">语义记忆层</text>
                    <text x="415" y="535" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">Vector Store</text>
                    <text x="415" y="546" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">1024-dim embeddings</text>

                    <rect x="515" y="500" width="170" height="50" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="520" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">情景记忆层</text>
                    <text x="600" y="535" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">Knowledge Graph</text>
                    <text x="600" y="546" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">Multi-hop reasoning</text>

                    <rect x="700" y="500" width="170" height="50" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="785" y="520" fill="#e2e8f0" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">程序记忆层</text>
                    <text x="785" y="535" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">User Profiling</text>
                    <text x="785" y="546" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">Long-term traits</text>

                    <!-- OceanBase Integration -->
                    <rect x="300" y="560" width="600" height="120" rx="8" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="300" y="560" width="600" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.4)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="600" y="585" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">OceanBase Database Integration</text>

                    <!-- Three Tables -->
                    <rect x="330" y="600" width="170" height="65" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="415" y="620" fill="white" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">memories 表</text>
                    <text x="415" y="635" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• id, memory, embedding</text>
                    <text x="415" y="646" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• user_id, metadata</text>
                    <text x="415" y="657" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• IVF_FLAT 索引</text>

                    <rect x="515" y="600" width="170" height="65" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="620" fill="white" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">user_memories +</text>
                    <text x="600" y="630" fill="white" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">graph_edges 表</text>
                    <text x="600" y="645" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 实体节点 + 关系边</text>
                    <text x="600" y="656" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• 多跳遍历支持</text>

                    <rect x="700" y="600" width="170" height="65" rx="4" fill="rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.3)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="785" y="620" fill="white" font-size="9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">user_profiles 表</text>
                    <text x="785" y="635" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• user_id (PK)</text>
                    <text x="785" y="646" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• profile_type</text>
                    <text x="785" y="657" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">• profile_data (JSON/TEXT)</text>

                    <!-- Cache Layer -->
                    <rect x="400" y="700" width="400" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="400" y="700" width="400" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(136, 19, 55, 0.4)" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="600" y="720" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Cache Layer (In-Memory)</text>
                    <text x="600" y="737" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">用户画像缓存 | 查询结果缓存 | TTL: 会话生命周期</text>

                    <!-- External Dependencies -->
                    <rect x="100" y="700" width="220" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="100" y="700" width="220" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.3)" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="210" y="720" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">LLM Services</text>
                    <text x="210" y="737" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Qwen / OpenAI (抽取/嵌入)</text>

                    <rect x="880" y="700" width="220" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a"/>
                    <rect x="880" y="700" width="220" height="50" rx="6" fill="rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4)" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <text x="990" y="720" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Manager API</text>
                    <text x="990" y="737" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">远程配置热更新</text>

                    <!-- Key -->
                    <rect x="350" y="780" width="500" height="50" rx="6" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <text x="600" y="800" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Key Design Patterns: Provider | Repository | Strategy | Factory | Observer | Decorator</text>
                    <text x="600" y="815" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Core Principles: Cognitive Economy | Multi-Level Memory | Intelligent Lifecycle | Hybrid Retrieval</text>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot emerald"></div>
                        <h3>Provider模式抽象</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>MemoryProviderBase：</strong>统一接口定义</li>
                        <li><strong>save_memory：</strong>异步写入API</li>
                        <li><strong>query_memory：</strong>语义检索API</li>
                        <li><strong>get_user_profile：</strong>画像获取API</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot violet"></div>
                        <h3>双模式设计</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>UserMemory：</strong>画像模式，长期特征</li>
                        <li><strong>AsyncMemory：</strong>对话模式，临时记忆</li>
                        <li><strong>工厂检测：</strong>enable_user_profile配置</li>
                        <li><strong>同步/异步：</strong>自动适配SDK类型</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-dot rose"></div>
                        <h3>性能优化</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Cache-Aside：</strong>95%画像缓存命中</li>
                        <li><strong>并行I/O：</strong>asyncio并发查询</li>
                        <li><strong>批量处理：</strong>16条嵌入向量批处理</li>
                        <li><strong>连接池：</strong>OceanBase连接复用</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>认知智能体记忆系统架构设计 • 生成日期: 2026-05-03 • 基于 OceanBase 的三级记忆架构</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; color: #475569;">Architecture Blueprint • C4 Model • Component-Level Design</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
